碳化硅存在着约250种结晶形态。<ref>{{cite book| url = http://books.google.com/?id=hJySnYNE3B0C| page = 3| title = Silicon carbide microelectromechanical systems for harsh environments| author =Cheung, Rebecca|
publisher = Imperial College Press| year = 2006| isbn = 1-86094-624-0}}</ref>由于碳化硅拥有一系列相似晶体结构的同质多型体使得碳化硅具有同质多晶的特点。这些多形体的晶体结构可被视为将特定几种二维结构以不同顺序层状堆积后得到的，因此这些多形体具有相同的化学组成和相同的二维结构，但它们的三维结构不同。<ref name=jap>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1063/1.358463|title = Large-band-gap SiC, III-V nitride, and II-VI ZnSe-based semiconductor device technologies|url = http://jap.aip.org/resource/1/japiau/v76/i3/p1363|year = 1994|author = Morkç, H.|journal = Journal of Applied Physics|volume = 76|issue = 3|pages = 1363|last2 = Strite|first2 = S.|last3 = Gao|first3 = G. B.|last4 = Lin|first4 = M. E.|last5 = Sverdlov|first5 = B.|last6 = Burns|first6 = M.|bibcode = 1994JAP....76.1363M}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

α-碳化硅(α-SiC)是这些多型体中最为常见的，它是在大于1700°C的温度下形成的，具有类似[[纤维锌矿|纤锌矿]]的六方晶体结构。具有类似[[钻石|钻石]]的[[立方晶系|闪锌矿晶体结构]]的β-碳化硅(β-SiC)则是在低于1700°C的条件下形成的。<ref name=muranaka>{{cite journal|author = Muranaka, T.|journal = Sci. Technol. Adv. Mater.|volume = 9|issue = 4|year = 2008| page = 044204|title =Superconductivity in carrier-doped silicon carbide| url = http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1468-6996/9/4/044204/stam8_4_044204.pdf| doi = 10.1088/1468-6996/9/4/044204|format=free download| bibcode=2008STAdM...9d4204M|display-authors = 1|last2 = Kikuchi|first2 = Yoshitake|last3 = Yoshizawa|first3 = Taku|last4 = Shirakawa|first4 = Naoki|last5 = Akimitsu|first5 = Jun}}</ref>β-碳化硅因其相较α-碳化硅拥有更高的比表面积，所以可用于非均相催化剂的负载体。

纯的碳化硅是无色的，工业用碳化硅由于含有铁等杂质而呈现棕色至黑色。晶体上彩虹般的光泽则是因为其表面产生的二氧化硅[[钝化|钝化层]]所致。

碳化硅高达2700°C的升华温度使得它适合作为制造[[轴承|轴承]]和高温熔炉的部件。它本身也具有较高的化学惰性。由于其相较于晶体硅具有更高的热电导率、[[电场|电场]]击穿强度和最大电流密度，所以在高功率的半导体材料方面具有更好的应用前景。<ref name=baliga>{{cite journal|last=Bhatnagar|first=M.|coauthors=Baliga, B.J.|url=http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/articleDetails.jsp?arnumber=199372|title=Comparison of 6H-SiC, 3C-SiC, and Si for power devices|journal=IEEE Transactions on Electron Devices|volume=40|issue=3|pages=645–655|doi=10.1109/16.199372|bibcode = 1993ITED...40..645B |date=March 1993}}</ref>此外碳化硅的[[热膨胀系数|热膨胀系数]]也非常低（4.0×10<sup>-6</sup>/K）同时也不会发生可能引起的不连续性热膨胀的相变。
 
=== 电导率 ===
在碳化硅中掺杂氮或磷可以形成[[半导体|n型半导体]]而掺杂[[铝|铝]]、[[硼|硼]]、[[镓|镓]]或[[铍|铍]]形成[[半导体|p型半导体]]。在碳化硅中大量掺杂硼、铝或氮可以使掺杂后的碳化硅具备数量级可与金属比拟的导电率。掺杂Al的3C-SiC、掺杂B的3C-SiC和6H-SiC的碳化硅都能在1.5K的温度下拥有超导性，<ref name=muranaka>{{cite journal|author = Muranaka, T.|journal = Sci. Technol. Adv. Mater.|volume = 9|issue = 4|year = 2008| page = 044204|title =Superconductivity in carrier-doped silicon carbide| url = http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1468-6996/9/4/044204/stam8_4_044204.pdf| doi = 10.1088/1468-6996/9/4/044204|format=free download| bibcode=2008STAdM...9d4204M|display-authors = 1|last2 = Kikuchi|first2 = Yoshitake|last3 = Yoshizawa|first3 = Taku|last4 = Shirakawa|first4 = Naoki|last5 = Akimitsu|first5 = Jun}}</ref><ref name=kriener>{{cite journal|author = Kriener, M.|journal = Sci. Technol. Adv. Mater.|volume = 9|issue = 4|year = 2008| page = 044205|title = Superconductivity in heavily boron-doped silicon carbide| url = http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1468-6996/9/4/044205/stam8_4_044205.pdf| doi =10.1088/1468-6996/9/4/044205|format=free download| bibcode=2008STAdM...9d4205K|display-authors = 1|last2 = Muranaka|first2 = Takahiro|last3 = Kato|first3 = Junya|last4 = Ren|first4 = Zhi-An|last5 = Akimitsu|first5 = Jun|last6 = Maeno|first6 = Yoshiteru|arxiv = 0810.0056 }}</ref>但掺杂Al和B的碳化硅两者的磁场行为有明显区别。掺杂铝的碳化硅和掺杂B的晶体硅一样都是[[第二类超导体|第二类超导体]]，但掺杂硼的碳化硅则是[[第一类超导体|第一类超导体]]。<ref>{{cite journal|author = Yanase, Y. and Yorozu, N.|format=free download|title =Superconductivity in compensated and uncompensated semiconductors|journal = Sci. Technol. Adv. Mater.|volume = 9|issue = 4|year = 2008| page = 044201|url = http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/1468-6996/9/4/044201/stam8_4_044201.pdf| doi =10.1088/1468-6996/9/4/044201|bibcode=2008STAdM...9d4201Y}}</ref>

== 用途 ==
=== 磨料和切割工具 ===
由于金刚砂的耐用性和低成本，在现代宝石加工中作为常用磨料使用。金刚砂凭借其硬度使它在制造业中诸如砂轮切割、搪磨、水刀切割和喷砂等磨削加工过程。将碳化硅粒子层压在纸上就能制成[[砂纸|砂纸]]和滑板的握带。

1982年由氧化铝和碳化硅须晶构成的超强复合材料问世，经过随后三年的发展这种复合材料走出实验室成为商品。1985年先进复合材料公司和Greenleaf公司推出了新的商品化切割工具，工具就是由氧化铝和碳化硅须晶组成的加强型复合材料所制造的。

=== 结构材料 ===
在二十世纪80至90年代，几个欧洲、日本和美国的高温燃气涡轮机研究项目对碳化硅做了研究，项目的目标均打算以碳化硅代替镍高温合金制造涡轮机叶片或喷嘴叶片。但这些项目无一实现量产，主要原因在于碳化硅材料的耐冲击性和断裂韧度低。

不同于其他陶瓷材料比如氧化铝和碳化硼，碳化硅可用于制造[[複合裝甲|複合裝甲]]（比如{{link-en|喬巴姆裝甲|Chobham armour}}）和[[護甲|防彈背心]]中的陶瓷板。

=== 天文学 ===
碳化硅具备的低热膨胀系数、高的硬度、刚性和热导率使其能够作为天文望远镜的镜面材料。通过化学气相沉积制造的直径达3.5米和2.7米的多晶碳化硅圆盘已被分别安装在[[赫歇尔空间天文台|赫歇尔空间天文台]]和[[同温层红外线天文台|同温层红外线天文台]]等几个大型天文望远镜上。<ref>{{cite news| title = The largest telescope mirror ever put into space| url = http://www.esa.int/esaSC/SEMC7W1PGQD_index_0.html| accessdate = 2009-06-06| publisher = European Space Agency| archive-date = 2012-10-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040023/http://www.esa.int/esaSC/SEMC7W1PGQD_index_0.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal| title =2.7-meter-diameter silicon carbide primary mirror for the SOFIA telescope| url =http://proceedings.spiedigitallibrary.org/proceeding.aspx?articleid=960284| bibcode =1994SPIE.2199..263P| author =Petrovsky| journal =Proc. SPIE| volume =2199| page =263-270| date =06/1994| author-separator =| author2 =G. Tolstoy| display-authors =2| last2 =| last3 =Lubarsky| first3 =Sergey V.| last4 =Khimitch| first4 =Yuri P.| last5 =Robb| first5 =Paul N.| doi =10.1117/12.176195| access-date =2013-02-06| archive-date =2014-04-19| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140419021732/http://proceedings.spiedigitallibrary.org/proceeding.aspx?articleid=960284| dead-url =no}}</ref>

=== 催化剂载体 ===
碳化硅本身的抗氧化性质和立方β-SiC所具有的大比表面积使其可作为非均相催化剂的载体。通过稻壳炭化合成的β-SiC已被用于作为非均相催化剂的载体应用于催化诸如正丁烷氧化生成[[顺丁烯二酸酐|顺丁烯二酸酐]]这类[[烃|烃类]]的氧化反应。<ref>{{cite book|page = 258| url = http://books.google.com/?id=s_1SomN_GVQC| title = Handbook of commercial catalysts: heterogeneous catalysts| author = Rase, Howard F.| publisher = CRC Press| year = 2000| isbn = 0-8493-9417-1}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal| url = http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2FBF02071177| title = High surface area silicon carbide from rice husk: A support material for catalysts| author = Singh, S. K.| journal = Reaction Kinetics and Catalysis Letters| volume = 54| issue = 1| year = 1995| page = 29| doi = 10.1007/BF02071177| last2 = Parida| first2 = K. M.| last3 = Mohanty| first3 = B. C.| last4 = Rao| first4 = S. B.| access-date = 2013-02-06| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304232040/http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2FBF02071177| dead-url = no}}</ref>

===石墨烯生长===
通过加热至高温，可在碳化硅的表面得到外延[[石墨烯|石墨烯]]。这种获取石墨烯的方法被认为有希望实现大规模合成具有实际应用的石墨烯<ref>{{cite book| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=08BWNlciXx4C&pg=SA19-PA2&lpg=SA19-PA2|chapter = 19. Epitaxial graphene|title=Handbook of Nanophysics |editor=Sattler, Klaus D.|publisher=Taylor and Francis|year=2010|isbn=1-4200-7538-1|author=de Heer|format=free download| author2 = Walt A.}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal| url = http://www.physics.gatech.edu/npeg/publications/DeHeerSSC07.pdf| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081209230924/http://www.physics.gatech.edu/npeg/publications/DeHeerSSC07.pdf| archivedate = 2008-12-09|title = Epitaxial graphene|accessdate = 2009-07-31|year=2007|author1=de Heer, Walt A. |author2=Berger, Claire |author3=Wu, Xiaosong |author4=First, Phillip N. |author5=Conrad, Edward H. |author6=Li, Xuebin |author7=Li, Tianbo |author8=Sprinkle, Michael |author9=Hass, Joanna |author10=Sadowski, Marcin L. |author11=Potemski, Marek |author12=Martinez, Gérard |journal=Solid State Communications|volume=143| issue = 1–2|pages=92–100|doi=10.1016/j.ssc.2007.04.023|format=free download|bibcode = 2007SSCom.143...92D}}</ref>。

===功率電子元件===
碳化硅是目前正在研究的[[半导体|半导体]]，已在快速切換、高溫及高電壓的應用上，進行前期的[[大量生產|大量生產]]。第一個可用的元件是[[肖特基二极管|肖特基二极管]]、之後是[[结型场效应管|结型场效应管]]及高速切換的[[功率MOSFET|功率MOSFET]]。目前正在開發[[双极性晶体管|双极性晶体管]]及[[晶閘管|晶閘管]]<ref name=baliga/>。

碳化矽元件商品化的主要問題是如何去除缺陷：包括邊緣位錯、螺旋位錯（空心和閉合）、三角形缺陷及基面位錯<ref>{{cite journal |journal=Mater. Res. Soc. Symp. Proc. |year=2006 |volume=911 |page=169 |title=Effects of defect types on the performance of devices fabricated on a 4H-SiC homoepitaxial layer |doi=10.1557/PROC-0911-B12-03 |last1=Chen |first1=H. |last2=Raghothamachar |first2=Balaji |last3=Vetter |first3=William |last4=Dudley |first4=Michael |last5=Wang |first5=Y. |last6=Skromme |first6=B.J.}}</ref>。因此，雖然有許多研究設法要改善特性，但最早期SiC材料的元件，其反向電壓阻隔能力不好<ref>{{cite journal |last=Madar |first=Roland |title=Materials science: Silicon carbide in contention |journal=Nature |volume=430 |issue=7003 |pages=974–975 |date=2004-08-26 |doi=10.1038/430974a |pmid=15329702 |bibcode=2004Natur.430..974M }}</ref>。除了晶體品質外，SiC和二氧化矽的界面問題也影響了SiC MOSFET及[[IGBT|IGBT]]的發展。[[滲氮|滲氮]]已大幅改善了介面問題，不過其機制還不清楚<ref>{{cite journal |year=2010 |journal=J. Of Elec. Mat. |volume=39 |issue=5 |pages=526–529 |title=MOS Characteristics of C-Face 4H-SiC  |doi=10.1007/s11664-010-1096-5 |last1=Chen |first1=Z. |last2=Ahyi |first2=A.C. |last3=Zhu |first3=X. |last4=Li |first4=M. |last5=Isaacs-Smith |first5=T. |last6=Williams |first6=J.R. |last7=Feldman |first7=L.C. |bibcode=2010JEMat..39..526C}}</ref>。

2008年已有第一個商品化的[[结型场效应管|JFET]]，額定1200V<ref name=reut>{{cite press release |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUS119430+05-May-2011+BW20110505 |archive-date=2016-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315023429/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUS119430+05-May-2011+BW20110505 |title=At 1200 V and 45 milliohms, SemiSouth introduces the industry’s lowest resistance SiC power transistor for efficient power management |agency=Reuters |date=2011-05-05 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>，之後是2011年第一個商品化的MOSFET，額定電壓1200 V。SiC的開關以及SiC[[肖特基二极管|肖特基二极管]]（SBD）有常見的TO-247及{{le|TO-220|TO-220}}封裝外，許多廠商也開始將SiC裸晶放在[[功率模組|功率模組]]中。

SiC SBD二極體已用在[[功率因数|功因修正]]電路上，以及[[絕緣柵雙極晶體管|IGBT]][[功率模組|功率模組]]中<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.cree.com/News-and-Events/Cree-News/Press-Releases/2011/January/110117-MOSFET |title=Cree launches industry’s first commercial silicon carbide power MOSFET; destined to replace silicon devices in high-voltage (≥ 1200 V) power electronics |publisher=Cree |date=2011-01-17 |df=dmy-all |access-date=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2016-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126064702/http://www.cree.com/News-and-Events/Cree-News/Press-Releases/2011/January/110117-MOSFET |dead-url=no }}</ref>。像是{{le|國際集成功率電子系統大會|International Conference on Integrated Power Electronics Systems}}（CIPS）等研討會也會定期報告有關SiC功率元件的技術驅勢。

日本部分新造的大功率[[交流傳動|交傳]]鐵路車輛，以碳化硅取代[[IGBT|IGBT]]用於牽引變流裝置（如[[新幹線E956型電力動車組|新幹線ALFA-X]]、[[台鐵EMU3000型電聯車|EMU3000]]和[[E235系|E235系]]），有助進一步減少車輛耗電。

SiC功率元件的主要挑戰有：
* 閘極驅動電路：SiC功率元件的閘極驅動電路和矽半導體的電路不同，閘極驅動電路的電壓是非對稱的（例如+20 V和−5 V）<ref>{{cite book |author=Meißer, Michael |title=Resonant Behaviour of Pulse Generators for the Efficient Drive of Optical Radiation Sources Based on Dielectric Barrier Discharges |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FiWkAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA94 |year=2013 |publisher=KIT Scientific Publishing |isbn=978-3-7315-0083-4 |page=94 |access-date=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428041310/https://books.google.com/books?id=FiWkAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA94 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 包裝：SiC [[裸晶|裸晶]]的功率密度比矽半導體要高，其溫度可以超過矽的上限150 °C。需要用到新的芯片連接技術（例如[[燒結|燒結]]）才能有效地將熱從元件帶出，並且確保存在可靠的互联结构 (Sintering are required to efficiently get the heat out of the devices and ensure a reliable interconnection. ) <ref>{{cite journal |title=Packaging Technologies for SiC Power Modules |author1=Horio, Masafumi |author2=Iizuka, Yuji |author3=Ikeda, Yoshinari |journal=Fuji Electric Review |volume=58 |issue=2 |pages=75–78 |year=2012 |url=http://www.fujielectric.com/company/tech/pdf/58-02/FER-58-2-075-2012.pdf |access-date=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2016-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701043708/http://www.fujielectric.com/company/tech/pdf/58-02/FER-58-2-075-2012.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

